Ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi by'akazi bya COVID-19
Ibirimo kugenzura ibyago byo mu kazi kubera COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ibirimo kugenzura ibyago mu kazi bigenda bihinduka bitewe n'aho akazi gakorerwa n'uburyo bwo gukora, bitewe n'uko ibipimo by'ibyago by'akazi, ubwandu bw'abaturage, n'ibikoresho bishobora gutuma abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19 bigenda bihinduka.
Ikigo cy'ubuvuzi n'umutekano mu kazi cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika (OSHA) kivuga ko gukora akazi k'ubuvuzi nta cyo bitwaye gutwara imodoka nyinshi n'abaturage cyangwa abakozi, kandi ko uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara bwa mbere bugomba gukurikizwa, nko gukaraba intoki, guhana abakozi bake mu rugo igihe barwaye, guhumeka, no gukora neza no gusukura imodoka.
Ibikorwa by'ubwandu bishobora kuba bikubiyemo abantu babaho cyangwa bagaragara ko bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ko abantu babaho cyangwa se bavuye mu mahanga.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bafite ubushobozi bwo gushyikirana n'abaturage, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu h'akazi hari abantu benshi, ahantu hakorerwa ibintu byinshi byo kugura.
Ibikorwa by'ubuyobozi, uretse kwirinda icyorezo cya mbere, birimo kwirinda impanuka z'indwara, kwirinda ko ibicurane byandura, kwirinda ko abana bakwirakwizwa n'ibinyabuzima, no kugira imyenda y'ubwirinzi ibaho iyo ubanye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi b'ubuzima n'abakozi b'inzego z'ubuvuzi bapfuye kubera ko bagaragaje ko bafite cyangwa bafite umuntu ushobora kuba afite COVID-19 nk'aho ari umubyibuho ukabije, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kurwara iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukwirakwiza umwuka, cyangwa gutwara, cyangwa gukoresha ibiyobyabwenge, umuntu ufite cyangwa ushobora kuba afite COVID-19.
Ingamba z'ibanze z'abakozi z'iki gihe z'ingengo y'imari zirimo ingamba z'ubugenzuzi z'ubugenzuzi, urugero nk'imyubakire myiza, n'ibikoresho by'isuku bifitanye isano n'akazi.
