b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo ihoraho mu gihe kirekire cyane mu gihe ikora mu buryo butandukanye (kugenzura ingirabuzimafatizo) mu mihaha, mu maraso, mu mutima, mu bwonko no mu mubiri.
ACE2 itera ingufu cyangwa ingufu z'ubuhinzi bwa angiotensin (ACE) igabanya ingendo za angiotensin-II kandi igabanya ang(1-7) bigatuma iba umuti ushobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'irembo mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'izindi koronavirusi.
Umuntu ashobora kwiyumvisha ko afite agaciro ka hACE2.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya 2 ihindura Angiotensin ni ingirabuzima fatizo irimo zinc kandi iboneka mu bice by'umubiri by'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ifite umurongo wa N-terminal peptidase M2 n'umurongo wa C-terminal collectrin wa amino acid transporter.
ACE2 ni ingirabuzimafatizo imwe y'ingirabuzimafatizo y'urukoba yo mu bwoko bwa I, ifite ubushobozi bwo gukora kandi iba mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu nda no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
Urubuga ACE2 rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ruhuza n'urubuga rwa transmembrane mu buryo butandukanye, buzwi nka sheddase, kandi imiterere y'amaraso y'amaraso y'ibinyabuzima iba ikomeje gushyirwa mu maraso, amaherezo igakura mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifitanye isano n'ubushakashatsi bw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze by'ubwoko bwa II bw'ibinyabuzima, enterocyte ntoya z'ibinyabuzima, ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima byinshi.
Ingingo z'umurongo wa ACE2 mRNA na zo zisanzwe ziboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'iburyo, mu gice cy'iburyo, no mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Icyiciro cya mbere cy'umurimo wa ACE2 ni ugushyira mu gaciro ku cyiciro cya kabiri cy'umurimo wa ACE.
ACE ihindura ingingo ya angiotensin I ikora ingingo ya angiotensin II.
ACE2 na yo ihindura amoko ya amino acide phenylalanine yitwa carboxyl-terminal ikomoka kuri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikoreshwa mu gutera intoki angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no gutuma habaho umubare w'andi peptides nka [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi ikora ku kintu cyitwa SLC6A19 cy'umushinga w'umwimerere wa amino acid kandi ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima, ACE2 ni ingomero imwe mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'izindi koronavirusi, urugero nka HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (umugera uteza SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (umugera utuma COVID-19 ibaho).
Ikindi cyakozwe ni ukuhuza spike S1 y'ibinyabuzima bya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 mu cyiciro cya ACE2 cy'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo zitaravamo endocytosis hamwe no gusubirana kwa virusi zombi hamwe no gushingira ku byiciro by'ingirabuzimafatizo biri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi myitozo ya S ishyiraho ingufu za proteine ya serine protease receptor TMPRSS2, ikaba iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo bwo kuvura. Niyo mpamvu twibaza ko kugabanya ingano ya ACE2, mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora kuba ingirakamaro mu kuvura iyi ndwara.
Icyakora, amatorero menshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura ibipimo by'ubuvuzi bw'indwara ya ACE n'ubuvuzi bwa ARB, byatanze inama yo gukomeza.
Ubushakashatsi n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku byagezweho ku itariki ya 11 Kamena 2012, bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha imiti ihagarika ingufu za ACE byaterwaga no kugabanya ibyago byo kurwara indwara ya Pneumonia ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'ubuvuzi".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kwandura indwara ya Pneumonia byagabanutse mu barwayi bavurwa n'abakijije ACE bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura indwara ya Pneumonia, cyane cyane mu barwayi b'amaraso n'abafite indwara y'umutima.
Gufata imiti igabanya ubukana bwa ACE byongeraga igihombo cy'ubwandu bw'impu z'amaguru, nubwo ibimenyetso byagabanutse cyane ku cyorezo cy'impu z'amaguru".
Recombinant ACE2 (rhACE2) y'umuntu ni umuti mushya ukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero, bityo ugafasha amaraso mu guhumeka no guhumeka mu bana bavuye mu ndwara z'ubuhumekero zirimo lipopolysaccharide.
Igice cy'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 ku muntu kiba mu minsi 10 gusa, igihe cy'akazi kigatangira mu minota 30 gusa, n'igihe cy'akazi kigakomera mu minsi 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti ukenewe mu bantu batemera imiti ihoraho ya renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa mu bantu bafite indwara ziterwa na angiotensin II. rhACE2 itemewe yagenzuwe mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero.
