Amakuru ya mbere agaragaza ko dosiye za ribavirin zifite akamaro ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 mu byiciro by'ubwonko.
Nitazoxanide yagiriwe inama mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buzima bwa bwite nyuma y'aho ibimenyetso byerekana ko umubare w'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 wagabanutse. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kubona poroteyine ya mbere y'umwirondoro binyuze mu muvuduko wa serine protease 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kuri SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu gukora na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine ndetse no kutagira azithromycin, bwagaragaje ko hari ibintu byinshi byabuzaga abaturage bacu bavuzi kubakira nta bushakashatsi bwakozwe. Oseltamivir ikwirakwiza SARS-CoV-2 mu byuma by'ubwonko kandi ifite uruhare runini mu kuvura COVID-19.
Kwirinda cytokine bishobora guteza akaga mu bindi bihe bibi bya COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kumenya uburyo bwo gutwara cytokine. Tocilizumab yongeye gushyirwa mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi n'Ikigo cy'Ubuzima cy'Igihugu cy'u Bushinwa nyuma yo kurangiza ubundi bushakashatsi buto.
Ni igikorwa cyo gukora icyiciro cya kabiri cy'igerageza ridakurikizwa mu gihugu cy'u Butaliyani kugira ngo rigaragaze ko abantu banduye kandi ko bafite indwara z'ubwonko.
Hamwe n'ibizamini by'imiterere y'amaraso y'ibinyabuzima bigenewe kumenya icyitwa cytokine, intego yayo ni ukugabanya ibyo bitero, bikaba bishobora gutuma abantu bamwe na bamwe barwara iyo ndwara bapfa.
